源<br />\n最緊要就係招降，可以招就招，招唔到就殺<br />\n好快佢就有兵無將，鳩玩都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬忠同潘乜，二者得一可安天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f51fc22797ea1469a8181417f4344a4cfd752c","tid":750653,"uid":16150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09dc1c9563c7f1fdd8f2b2f2336b66059bad4223","tid":750653,"uid":175458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"048f58ae301774f5fbbc6084e267cd0cb31e3d9b","tid":750653,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:47:22.000Z","msg":"啱啱買咗黎玩，英雄集結開波<br />\n用古代武將喺巴蜀起家<br />\n一開頭同大耳賊結盟諗住有個幫手<br />\n點知佢好快就打爆咗曹操同孫堅<br />\n而我拎曬巴蜀同西涼嗰時佢已經佔曬所有地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：爆過三國志13高級"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:03:06.000Z","msg":"古代武將 一隊楊大眼已經輕鬆搞掂幾隊一線武將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係趙雲煩左d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"張良放計略都屈死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb659409658a4165228b98a3b73004f4a918ff7","tid":750653,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fcde9b4e59bd542663befd55de28c5bf60260e9","tid":750653,"uid":49216,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:05:57.000Z","msg":"兩座近既城炒下糧賺錢<br />\n起會爆火果個陷阱再用廢將1兵去自爆<br />\n用勁將守路口，後面幾枝弓抽水<br />\n如果削極兵都守唔到要棄城就拎走晒錢同糧先<br />\n一路睇住佢邊啲城空虛，見無咩兵/將就突襲果啲城<br />\n突到就試下守，突唔到就打爆建築先走當削佢兵，削佢資源<br />\n最緊要就係招降，可以招就招，招唔到就殺<br />\n好快佢就有兵無將，鳩玩都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬忠同潘乜，二者得一可安天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:11:19.000Z","msg":"我記得研究技能有得拎佢兩個招技<br />\n其實有冇用"},{"pid":"ff8f51ef10b3c1995522ac56ed6f9c50776973c3","tid":750653,"uid":15849